ZH: 我买了一套玻璃杯。
EN: I bought a set of glass cups.

ZH: 她把玻璃杯放在桌子上。
EN: She placed the glass cup on the table.

ZH: 这个玻璃杯很脆。
EN: This glass cup is very fragile.

ZH: 他不小心打破了一个玻璃杯。
EN: He accidentally broke a glass cup.

ZH: 我想喝一杯水，请给我一个玻璃杯。
EN: I want to have a drink, please give me a glass cup.

ZH: 我家有一整排玻璃杯。
EN: My house has a row of glass cups.

ZH: 这个玻璃杯非常漂亮。
EN: This glass cup is very beautiful.

ZH: 爸爸喜欢喝咖啡，他有很多玻璃杯。
EN: Dad likes to drink coffee, he has many glass cups.

ZH: 请小心，不要打碎玻璃杯。
EN: Please be careful, don't break the glass cup.

ZH: 这个玻璃杯的外形设计很独特。
EN: The design of this glass cup is very unique.

ZH: 我用玻璃杯喝了一杯果汁。
EN: I drank a glass of juice with a glass cup.

ZH: 她从柜子里拿出一只玻璃杯。
EN: She took out a glass cup from the cabinet.

ZH: 这个维也纳咖啡店的招牌是一个玻璃杯。
EN: The signboard of this Vienna coffee shop is a glass cup.

ZH: 我喜欢用玻璃杯泡茶。
EN: I like to brew tea with a glass cup.

ZH: 这家餐厅所有的饮料都是用玻璃杯供应的。
EN: All the drinks in this restaurant are served in glass cups.

ZH: 这个杯子既是玻璃杯又是保温杯。
EN: This cup is both a glass cup and a thermos cup.

ZH: 玻璃杯看起来很简单，但是制作起来很讲究。
EN: Glass cups look simple, but they require delicate craftsmanship.

ZH: 奶奶把一双玻璃杯作为我们的结婚礼物。
EN: Grandma gave us a pair of glass cups as a wedding gift.

ZH: 昨晚，我不小心打碎了一个玻璃杯。
EN: Last night, I accidentally broke a glass cup.

ZH: 这个玻璃杯的材料非常环保。
EN: The material of this glass cup is very environmentally friendly.
